snippet.title: Amber Alert after Milwaukee homicide | FOX6 News Milwaukee
snippet.description:
A statewide Amber Alert for a 2-year-old boy has been canceled after the child was located safe. However, police now say the homicide of an 18-year-old Milwaukee woman is related to this case. https://bit.ly/3jGrwTK
